01:51.485 --> 01:57.658
Shrek

02:45.081 --> 02:47.752
Beware

03:16.903 --> 03:18.157
Stay out

03:38.092 --> 03:39.552
I think he's in here.

03:39.802 --> 03:40.845
All right. Lets get it!

03:41.095 --> 03:43.848
Hold on. Do you know what that thing can do to you?

03:44.098 --> 03:48.394
Yeah. He'll groan into your bones for his brains.

03:48.644 --> 03:51.981
Well actually that would be a giant.

03:52.231 --> 03:55.234
Now Ogres, huh, they are much worse.

03:55.484 --> 03:59.655
They'll make a soup from your freshly peeled skin.

03:59.906 --> 04:03.576
They'll chew your livers,
squeeze the jelly from your eyes.

04:03.826 --> 04:05.286
Actually, it's quite good on toast.

04:05.536 --> 04:07.788
Back, back beast, back!

04:08.039 --> 04:12.335
I warned you!

04:13.503 --> 04:17.798
Right.

04:31.229 --> 04:34.774
This is the part, where you run away.

04:35.024 --> 04:39.320
Yeah!

04:41.280 --> 04:45.868
And stay out.

04:46.744 --> 04:52.250
Wanted. Fairytale creatures.

04:55.586 --> 05:01.342
Right, this one is full. Take it away.

05:03.845 --> 05:05.137
Give me that.

05:05.388 --> 05:08.099
Your fine days are over.
-25 pieces of silver for the witch.

05:08.349 --> 05:13.396
Next.
-Come on.

05:13.646 --> 05:17.567
Sit down there! And be quiet!

05:17.817 --> 05:19.986
This cage is so small.

05:20.236 --> 05:22.488
You wouldn't turn me in.
I'll never be stubborn again. I can change.

05:22.738 --> 05:24.031
Please, give me another chance.

05:24.282 --> 05:26.033
Oh, shut up!

05:26.284 --> 05:27.076
Next.

05:27.326 --> 05:27.827
What do we got?

05:28.077 --> 05:29.620
This little wooden puppet.

05:29.871 --> 05:35.042
I'm not a puppet, I'm a real boy.

05:35.293 --> 05:37.420
Five shillings for the possessed toy.
Take it away.

05:37.670 --> 05:39.463
No! Please, don't let them do it!

05:39.714 --> 05:41.090
Next. What do you got?

05:41.340 --> 05:44.385
Well, I've got a talking donkey!

05:44.635 --> 05:45.469
Right.

05:45.720 --> 05:48.723
Well that's good for ten schillings,
if you can prove it.

05:48.973 --> 05:53.519
Oh, go ahead fella.

05:53.769 --> 05:54.896
Well?

05:55.146 --> 05:57.398
He's just a li..., just a little nervous.

05:57.648 --> 06:00.109
He's really quite a chatterbox.

06:00.359 --> 06:01.402
You boneheaded donkey!

06:01.652 --> 06:02.862
That's it. I have heard enough. Guards!

06:03.112 --> 06:05.907
No, no, he talks, he does!

06:06.157 --> 06:08.618
I can talk. I love to talk.

06:08.868 --> 06:12.413
I've talked to...

06:12.663 --> 06:18.544
Get her out of my sight!
-No, no, I swear!

06:22.173 --> 06:24.884
Hey, I can fly.
-He can fly! -He can fly!

06:25.134 --> 06:27.762
He can talk!
-That's right, fool!

06:28.012 --> 06:30.806
Now I'm a flying, talking donkey!

06:31.057 --> 06:32.850
You might have seen house fly,
maybe even a superfly.

06:33.100 --> 06:39.941
But I bet you ain't never seen a donkey fly!

06:42.860 --> 06:47.156
Seize him!

06:57.708 --> 07:03.589
Get him! This way! Hurry!

07:05.800 --> 07:09.804
You there. Ogre.
-I.

07:10.054 --> 07:11.597
By the order of lord Farquaad.

07:11.848 --> 07:14.183
I am authorized to place you
both under arrest.

07:14.433 --> 07:20.439
And transport you to designated
resettlement facility.

07:20.690 --> 07:22.149
Oh really?

07:22.400 --> 07:27.238
You and what army?

07:35.705 --> 07:37.248
Can I say something to you?

07:37.498 --> 07:40.751
Listen, you were really, really something,
back there. Incredible.

07:41.002 --> 07:43.963
Are you talking to...

07:44.213 --> 07:46.382
...me?

07:46.632 --> 07:47.842
Yes, I was talking to you.

07:48.092 --> 07:50.644
Can I just tell you that you were
really great back there with those guards.

07:50.795 --> 07:51.721
They thought that was all over there.

07:51.971 --> 07:55.683
And then you showed up and BAM. There was tripping
on over themselves like babes in the woods.

07:55.933 --> 07:57.468
That really made me feel good to see that.

07:57.518 --> 07:58.769
Oh, that's great. Really.

07:59.020 --> 08:00.062
Man, it's good to be free.

08:00.313 --> 08:06.135
Now, why don't you go celebrate your freedom
with your own friends?

08:06.485 --> 08:07.904
But I...

08:08.154 --> 08:09.488
I don't have any friends.

08:09.739 --> 08:12.116
And I'm not going out there by myself.

08:12.366 --> 08:13.618
Hey wait a minute. I have a great idea...

08:13.868 --> 08:15.077
I'll stick with you.

08:15.328 --> 08:16.454
You and me in green fighting machine.

08:16.704 --> 08:22.110
Together we'll scare the spin if anybody crosses us.

08:23.503 --> 08:26.088
Oh, a, that was really scary.

08:26.339 --> 08:29.709
Maybe you don't mine me saying. If that don't work,
your breath will certainly do the job done, 'cause...

08:29.759 --> 08:32.111
you definitively need some tic-tac or something,

08:32.260 --> 08:34.722
'cause your breath stinks!

08:34.972 --> 08:36.474
Man you've ???  my note!

08:36.724 --> 08:39.268
Just like the time...

08:39.519 --> 08:40.852
...and then I ate some rotten berries.

08:41.102 --> 08:43.188
Man I had some strong gases leaking
out of my but that day.

08:43.438 --> 08:47.026
Why are you following me?

08:47.276 --> 08:50.446
I'll tell you why.

08:50.696 --> 08:52.657
'Cause I'm all alone,

08:52.907 --> 08:56.786
there is no one here, beside me.

08:57.036 --> 09:04.001
My problems have all gone.
There's no one to derive me.

09:04.252 --> 09:09.006
But you got to have free ...
-Stop singing!

09:09.257 --> 09:11.801
Well, it's no wonder, you don't have any friends.

09:12.051 --> 09:14.628
Wow! Only a true friend would be that truly honest.

09:14.679 --> 09:16.222
Listen! Little donkey.

09:16.472 --> 09:20.434
Take a look at me! What am I?

09:20.685 --> 09:23.771
A...

09:24.021 --> 09:24.689
...really tall?

09:24.939 --> 09:30.278
No! I'm an Ogre.
You know, grab your torch and pitchforks.

09:30.528 --> 09:33.573
Doesn't that bother you?

09:33.823 --> 09:35.491
Nope.

09:35.741 --> 09:37.785
Really?
-Really really.

09:38.035 --> 09:38.828
Oh?

09:39.078 --> 09:41.080
Man, I like you. What's your name?

09:41.330 --> 09:44.500
A..., Shrek.

09:44.750 --> 09:46.169
Shrek?!

09:46.419 --> 09:47.378
But do you know, what I like about you, Shrek?

09:47.628 --> 09:50.381
You've got that kind of:
"I don't care what nobody thinks of me" thing.

09:50.631 --> 09:55.970
I like that, I respect that, Shrek. You're all right.

09:56.220 --> 09:57.847
Uh, look at that.

09:58.097 --> 10:00.141
Who would wanna live in
a place like that?

10:00.391 --> 10:02.602
That would be my home.

10:02.852 --> 10:07.607
Oh, it is lovely. Just beautiful.
You know you're quite a decorator.

10:07.857 --> 10:10.276
It's amazing what you did with such a modest budget.

10:10.526 --> 10:16.741
I like that boulder. That is a nice boulder.

10:19.368 --> 10:21.454
I guess, you don't entertain much, do you?

10:21.704 --> 10:23.539
I like my privacy.

10:23.789 --> 10:25.833
You know I do to.
That's another thing, we have in common.

10:26.083 --> 10:29.170
Like I hate it when you got somebody in your face.
You try to give them a hint and they won't leave.

10:29.420 --> 10:34.842
And then there's that big occurred silence,
you know?

10:35.801 --> 10:38.221
Can I stay with you?
-What?

10:38.471 --> 10:40.848
Can I stay with you, please.

10:41.098 --> 10:43.184
Of course!
-Really?

10:43.434 --> 10:45.770
No.
-Please! I don't want to go back there.

10:46.020 --> 10:48.147
You don't how is like to be concerned like a freak.

10:48.397 --> 10:50.942
Well..., maybe you do.
But that's why we have to stick together!

10:51.192 --> 10:53.277
You got to let me stay! Please! Please!

10:53.528 --> 10:55.613
OK, OK.

10:55.863 --> 10:58.199
-But one night only.
-Huh, thank you!

10:58.449 --> 10:59.617
A, what are you do... No!

10:59.867 --> 11:02.453
This is going to be fun.
We can stay up late, swap the manly stories.

11:02.703 --> 11:03.829
And in the morning...

11:04.080 --> 11:06.999
I'm making waffles.

11:07.250 --> 11:09.001
Where do I sleep?

11:09.252 --> 11:11.754
Outside!

11:12.004 --> 11:15.716
Oh, a, I guess that's cool. You know,
I don't know you and you don't know me...

11:15.967 --> 11:19.470
... so I guess, outside is best for me.

11:19.720 --> 11:24.016
Here I go.

11:24.267 --> 11:28.145
Good night.

11:28.396 --> 11:32.066
I do like that half door.
I'm a donkey all alone outside.

11:32.316 --> 11:37.280
Sit by myself outside, I guess.

11:37.363 --> 11:45.454
I'm all alone, there's no one here beside me.

12:46.974 --> 12:53.564
-I thought, I told you to stay outside.
-I am outside.

12:58.528 --> 13:01.489
Well James. This is far from the farm,
but what choice do we have?

13:01.739 --> 13:05.076
It's not...

13:05.326 --> 13:07.620
What a lovely bed.
-Got you!

13:07.870 --> 13:13.292
I found some cheese. Awful stuff.

13:13.543 --> 13:15.586
-Is that you Gordon?
-How did you know?

13:15.837 --> 13:21.876
Enough! What are you doing in my house?

13:22.260 --> 13:24.887
Oh, no, no, no... Death prods off the table!

13:25.137 --> 13:30.560
Where would we supposed to put her.
The bed's taken.

13:31.686 --> 13:32.478
What?

13:32.728 --> 13:37.900
I live in a swamp. I've put up signs.
I'm a terrifying Ogre!

13:38.150 --> 13:44.282
What do I have to do, to get a little privacy?

13:44.532 --> 13:51.747
Oh, no! No, no!

13:59.422 --> 14:05.678
What are you doing in my swamp?

14:10.766 --> 14:14.270
All right, get out of here. All of you.
Move it! Come on, let's go.

14:14.520 --> 14:17.023
And hurry up, hurry up.

14:17.273 --> 14:23.154
No, no, not there. Not there!

14:24.280 --> 14:26.824
Hey don't look at me. I didn't invite them.

14:27.074 --> 14:29.702
Oh gosh, no one invited us.
-What?

14:29.952 --> 14:32.330
