20:23.181 --> 20:25.099
Aha, that's the place.

20:25.349 --> 20:30.688
Do you think maybe he's compensating for something.

20:32.815 --> 20:37.528
Hey, hey wait up Shrek!

20:39.238 --> 20:41.532
-Hey, you!
-No, no!

20:41.782 --> 20:43.451
Wait a second.

20:43.701 --> 20:49.540
Look, I'm not gonna eat you. I just...

21:20.279 --> 21:24.116
It's quiet.

21:24.367 --> 21:28.538
Too quiet.

21:28.788 --> 21:31.457
Where is everybody?

21:31.707 --> 21:36.212
Hey look at this.

22:20.548 --> 22:22.717
Wow!

22:22.967 --> 22:28.514
-Let's do that again.
-No. no.

22:38.941 --> 22:40.902
All right.
You're going the right way for smack bottom.

22:41.152 --> 22:43.404
Sorry about that.

22:43.654 --> 22:46.657
That champion should have the honor, no, no...

22:46.908 --> 22:56.167
...the privilege to go forth and rescue the lovely
princess Fiona from the fireing keep of the dragon.

22:56.417 --> 23:03.674
If for any reason the winner is unsuccessful,
the first runner up will take his place.

23:03.925 --> 23:06.219
And so on, and so forth.

23:06.469 --> 23:15.061
Some of you may die,
but it's a sacrifice I'm willing to make.

23:15.311 --> 23:17.104
Applause.

23:17.355 --> 23:23.110
Let the tournament begin.

23:25.696 --> 23:28.324
What is that?

23:28.574 --> 23:29.992
Ugh, it's hideous.

23:30.243 --> 23:33.120
Oh, that's not very nice.

23:33.371 --> 23:35.581
It's just a donkey.

23:35.831 --> 23:37.124
Indeed.

23:37.375 --> 23:42.463
Knights! New plan. The one, who kills the Ogre,
will be named champion.

23:42.713 --> 23:44.632
How about him.

23:44.882 --> 23:50.012
Oh, hey. Now, come on.

23:50.388 --> 23:54.767
Can't we just settle this over a pint?

23:55.017 --> 23:56.352
No?

23:56.602 --> 23:59.438
All right then.

23:59.689 --> 24:03.985
Come on.

24:32.430 --> 24:37.894
Hey Shrek! Let me, let me!

24:46.736 --> 24:52.033
The chair! Give him the chair!

25:14.055 --> 25:16.057
Thank you. Thank you, very much.

25:16.307 --> 25:20.478
I'm here until Thursday. Try the wheel!

25:25.274 --> 25:26.984
Shall I give the order sir?

25:27.235 --> 25:30.780
No. I have a better idea.

25:31.030 --> 25:35.910
People of Duloc. I give you our champion!

25:36.160 --> 25:38.079
What?

25:38.329 --> 25:40.206
Congratulation, Ogre.

25:40.456 --> 25:44.085
You've won the honor of embarking
on a great and noble quest.

25:44.335 --> 25:46.963
Quest? I'm already on a quest.

25:47.213 --> 25:48.840
A quest to get my swamp back!

25:49.090 --> 25:51.968
-Your swamp?
-Yeah, my swamp!

25:52.218 --> 25:55.638
Where you dumped those fairytale creatures.

25:55.888 --> 25:57.014
Indeed.

25:57.265 --> 25:59.267
All right Ogre, I'll make you a deal.

25:59.517 --> 26:03.771
Go on this quest for me and
I'll give you your swamp back.

26:04.021 --> 26:06.315
Exactly the way it was?

26:06.566 --> 26:08.818
Down to the last slime covered toast tool.

26:09.068 --> 26:13.364
-And the squatters?
-As good as gone.

26:16.325 --> 26:19.954
What kind of quest?

26:20.204 --> 26:20.746
Ok, let me get this straight!

26:20.997 --> 26:25.293
We gonna go find the dragon and rescue a princess
just so Farquaad will give you back the swamp,

26:25.293 --> 26:27.628
which you only don't have, 'cause he filled it
with full of freaks on the first place.

26:27.879 --> 26:29.422
